-- Russia c.bank shifts rouble's trading band by 35 kopecks
-- By Lidia Kelly and Alexander Winning
-- Tue Oct 28, 2014 03:09AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Oct 28 (Reuters) - Russia's central bank said on Tuesday it had shifted the rouble's trading band by 35 kopecks a day earlier, following market interventions to curb the pace of currency's decline.

